{"badges":["TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"content":["Place water in mixing bowl and heat <nobr>8 min\/Varoma\/speed 1<\/nobr>. Meanwhile, place salmon fillets in Varoma dish and season with 2 pinches salt and 2 pinches pepper. Place 2 slices lemon on each salmon fillet.","Once water has heated, place covered Varoma dish into position then steam <nobr>8 min\/Varoma\/speed 1<\/nobr>. Meanwhile,  prepare courgetti using a spiralizer (see tip) and transfer to Varoma tray. Season courgetti with 2 pinches salt, 2 pinches pepper and stir through grated lemon zest.","Insert Varoma tray with reserved seasoned courgetti and steam for a further <nobr>3 min\/Varoma\/speed 1<\/nobr>. Serve immediately with a drizzle of olive oil over courgetti if desired."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"","content":["1000 g water","1 lemon, zest finely grated, then cut in 8 slices","4 pinches fine sea salt","4 pinches ground black pepper","4 fresh salmon fillets, boneless (approx. 140 g each)","3 courgettes (to make approx. 550 g courgetti)","olive oil, for serving (optional)"]}],"id":"r131724","imageLink":"https:\/\/4.bp.blogspot.com\/-GNLgY-b39Dc\/XZVRpr6ffcI\/AAAAAAAAdRQ\/wFIl7IG6ftcH-k7IYq04G_V_moc3H7esACLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_tfvItFZRfHecytfB.png","title":"Steamed Salmon with Courgetti","publishedAt":"2016-12-26T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"35.7 g","fat":"18.1 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"4 g","calories":"1345 kJ \/ 322 kcal"},"usefulItems":"spiralizer or julienne peeler","hintsAndTricks":["If you don't have a spiralizer, use a julienne peeler or peel courgette into ribbons with a standard peeler and slice thinly lengthways.","Test that the salmon is fully cooked before serving.","For a 'help yourself' family meal, once the salmon and courgetti are cooked, break the salmon up and stir into the courgetti in a large serving bowl adding a drizzle of oil. You could also add some paprika, to taste, if desired."],"basicInfo":["easy","20m","35m","4 portions"]}